<th colspan="2" style="background-color:#B0C4DE;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Units involved</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">
<p>Lake &amp; Wellesley:<sup id="cite_ref-cooper315_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-cooper315-1">[1]</a></sup></p>
<dl>
<dd>
<div class="plainlist">
<ul>
<li>4 regiments European cavalry</li>
<li>8 regiments Native cavalry</li>
<li>2 regiments British infantry</li>
<li>17 sepoy battalions</li>
<li>Artillery</li>
</ul>
</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</td>
<td style="width:50%;padding-left:0.25em">Shock Infantry forces</td>
